<div class="page-header">
<h1>Fireworks Idle Client</h1>
<small>Help retain your license hold through fireworks idle client</small>
</div>
<div class="">
  <h2>Mechanism</h2>
  <p>
    <ul>
      <li>Download and install the client</li>
      <li>Configure the client so it points to your fireworks server</li>
      <li>That's it</li>
    </ul>
  </p>
  <p>
    The client will report your idle activities to your fireworks server. If fireworks has set some license server to be monitored for idle activity, you should be spared if you installed the client and you haven't been idle for over 30 minutes.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="">
  <h2>Download Idle Client</h2>
  <ul class="thumbnails">
    <li class="span4">
      <div class="thumbnail">
