          <p>Comming soon...<p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="span4">
      <div class="thumbnail">
        <img src="http://placehold.it/400x300" alt="" \>
        <div class="caption">
          <h3>Mac OS X</h3>
          <p><%= link_to 'Mac OS X 10.8',welcome_download_client_path(:type => 'Mac Os X'), :class=>'btn btn-primary' %></p>
          <h4>Requirement</h4>
          <p>Mac OS X 10.8</p>
          <h4>Instructions</h4>
          <p>Download, unzip, copy the App file to Application file and start</p>
